          "content": {
            "size": 18892,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"success\":true,\"data\":{\"id\":\"16f69ef1-6b01-40ca-99e6-0c23e977a391\",\"workspaceId\":\"5fba167c-a7c9-4e4d-8646-0cb71fda4717\",\"userId\":\"82f8b41c-3966-4128-9a42-8d81e44b3298\",\"presetId\":\"d0cacdce-0af7-45d0-9302-84c8163d0c49\",\"presetName\":\"Simple Business\",\"content\":\"PROJECT_TITLE:\\nAgent Frameworks Are Setup Porn, Not Revenue Generators\\n\\nCAROUSEL_TEXTLINES:\\nSLIDE 1 (textLines):\\nAgent Frameworks Are Setup Porn, Not Revenue Generators\\n\\nSLIDE 2 (textLines):\\nAgent frameworks are the ultimate setup porn.\\n\\nImpressive dashboards.\\nComplex hierarchies.\\nZero revenue.\\n\\nYou're not building a business... you're building an expensive hobby.\\n\\nSLIDE 3 (textLines):\\nYou know what makes money?\\n\\nWriting better emails.\\nCreating better offers.\\nSolving real problems.\\n\\nYou know what doesn't?\\n\\nA Telegram bot managing your Hermes agent inside your Paperclip dashboard.\\n\\nSLIDE 4 (textLines):\\nThe engagement trap:\\n\\nFrameworks like this go viral because they look impressive.\\n\\nTerminal windows. Complex dashboards.\\n\\nBut impressive вү  profitable.\\n\\nIt's setup porn, not business strategy.\\n\\nSLIDE 5 (textLines):\\nHuman companies look the way they do because of human limitations.\\n\\nDunbar numbers. Management capacity.\\n\\nAI has none of these constraints.\\n\\nSo why copy paste the org chart?\\n\\nSLIDE 6 (textLines):\\nThe wake up call:\\n\\nIf you're spending more time configuring agents than serving customers, you've already lost.\\n\\nSimplify. Ship. Repeat.\\n\\nThat's the only framework that matters.\",\"aspectRatio\":\"4:5\",\"mode\":\"follow\",\"customPrompt\":null,\"slideCount\":6,\"generatedPages\":[{\"html\":\"<link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"width: 1080px; height: 1350px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; background-color: #000000;\\\">\\n    <!-- Backgr